snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance - Armor & RPG
snippet.description:
We are presenting new insides of the development of Kingdom Come: Deliverance! Find out how our extensive RPG system and our sophisticated armor layer system works. Furthermore we are talking about item quality and survival elements in Kingdom Come: Deliverance. Take a look! 

To play the Beta version of the game go to https://www.kingdomcomerpg.com/en/get-the-game

Discuss the video on our Forum! http://forum.kingdomcomerpg.com/t/video-update-armor-and-rpg/28812

Check our updated merchandise shop https://www.czechbeergifts.com/producers/kingdom-come-deliverance/ to get nice T-shirts or our exclusive mug! 

Special thanks to Jonáš Chmátal and Jiří Kothera.
